<!-- Node: "The RUST online discussion channel" -->
<div class="body_box_header">The RUST online discussion channel</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/3" title="View user profile.">Tycho</a> on Saturday, July 17, 2004 - 13:32</small><br /><br />
To anyone who might be interessted, RUST has opened a new discussion channel on the Gamesurge IRC network.<br />
If you have questions that needs immediate attention or you just want to speak with the people who runs this site, check out the channel.<br />
<br />
To access, connect to <a href="irc://irc.gamesurge.net">irc.gamesurge.net</a> and join channel #rust.<br />
<br />
If you do not have an IRC client, <a href="http://www.mirc.com">mIRC</a> and <a href="http://www.xchat.org">X-Chat</a> are both excellent choises.<br />
<br />
We'll see you there.
<br /><br />
