<a href = "http://www.doom3.com/">DOOM3.com</a> used to be just one page with screenshots, trailer, desktops and preorder link. Now you can actually enter the site and read game overview, see the screenshots for both pc and xbox, including wallpapers and other things. Head over to <a href = "http://www.doom3.com/">www.doom3.com</a> and check it out.
